<div class="com-share" data-id="3015" data-title="《40 亿投资魅族，阿里巴巴联合小一号的小米冲进了手机市场》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/3015/medium/3015.jpg?1436635793" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/3015.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
